<br>
The real problem lies in the fact that a single source of information is needed for each server.  A place that ALL people will be directed to and use as a resource.<br>
<br>
Given that Planes and their spawn are a limited commodity, i can understand the angst felt here by Gwynet, yet -as has been said- this board is not likely widely used by players across the world universally.<br>
<br>
Wjhat we need is a single site, a single source.  A calendar system that is easy to us and that contains information that will not be lost.  Times should be listed as well, estimated times of arrival and departure.  That ways situations of time-zone differences will not be an issue.  I believe the current calendar is simply a message board.  A true <a href="http://oeuguild.virtualave.net/calendar.pl">calendar</a> is what is required.<br>
<br>
I would encourage all of the guild leaders to comment on this, as such a site would benefit all as well as bringing a measure of stability and peace between the guilds.<br>
<br>
The problem of course being how to make it 'universally accepted'.  So, post your thoughts.  We have nothing to lose and a great deal to gain. <p><small><i>Venerato Quod Equitas</i>,
